https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hqy9d1ZDdp4upeBmKcmP4Mf9WlG.jpg Ardal O'Hanlon returns to his home country with a sell out show at Dublin's Olympia Theatre for this specially recorded show. Featuring brand new material from his 2007 tour, this DVD marks 10 years since Ardal's last stand-up tour. The show won rave reviews and marks a triumphant return to stand up comedy for one of Ireland's best loved comics. Ardal O'Hanlon - Live in Dublin
